title: Couple pose for emotional break-up photo shoot | Daily Mail Online
text: The bitter end! Former couple poses for an emotional BREAK-UP SHOOT to commemorate their three-and-a-half-year relationship Harrison Bach, 22, invited ex-girlfriend Jackie, 20, to take part in a shoot to mark their breakup The student from Michigan was inspired by friends who have professional couples photographs done when they are still together The high school sweethearts split up in 2015 after it became a long distance relationship when they went to college They reunited on New Year's Eve to take the photographs and said they found the experience emotional Published: 04:36 GMT, 25 February 2017 | Updated: 04:36 GMT, 25 February 2017 70 shares
